QuestData.Title: Hero's Call: Jade Forest!
QuestData.Description:
All able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Stormwind Keep in Stormwind.
Grand Admiral Jes-Tereth is assembling a team for a high priority mission.
Head to Stormwind Keep immediately to be briefed.
Glory to the Alliance!
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Grand Admiral Jes-Tereth in Stormwind Keep.
QuestData.RewardText:
Our role is of utmost importance, $n.
Admiral Taylor and his flagship have gone missing.... More importantly, the young Prince was with him, and it is our primary objective to bring him back home safely.
